	<h1 class="title">这本年历一直都在展示美好肉体，今年却选择展示女性的强大内心</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Vanessa Friedman</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-11 12:39:55 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18793/medium/18793.jpg?1449664353" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="18793" data-title="《这本年历一直都在展示美好肉体，今年却选择展示女性的强大内心》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/18793/medium/18793.jpg?1449664353" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/18793.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
